data.description: Let’s start with something exciting! Seller will pay $12,000 towards your closing costs and/or a rate buy-down!   Welcome to paradise! This STUNNER will WOW you! Step inside & take it all in! High ceilings, tons of windows, & warm wood floors all make it instantly feel like HOME! Double islands in the kitchen & open concept living make it perfect for entertaining! Don't skip the primary bedroom! Tray ceilings, a lounge area, & beautiful windows create the perfect ambiance for peaceful evenings. Head into the primary bath. A generously sized walk in shower & soaking tub will become your own private spa. Soak away the long days and leave all your cares behind. Head upstairs & peek at the large bonus over the garage! Make it yours just in time for GAME DAY! Leave all your worries behind as you share good food, laughter & your favorite team with friends or family!
